{"tid":874191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人妻玩很大！女兒不是老公的　竟也不是小王的","createTime":"2018-10-24T04:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-24T07:28:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d79b9af66ff63311a90c39c0b8c69430a3794150","tid":874191,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181024/640_20fec46b9c540130747b2e7164e49e83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181024%2F640_20fec46b9c540130747b2e7164e49e83.jpg&h=0d575339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這位太太會不會太扯...<br />\n<br />\n《自由時報》報導，桃園李姓男子愛女即將滿周歲，卻在此時聽聞一項不幸消息，原來是他的吳姓妻子對他說「女兒不是你的」，並自爆受孕期間曾和37歲陳男發生關係，李男怒告老婆和小王通姦。<br />\n<br />\n陳男到案時喊冤，表示「吳女自稱已離婚」，且經親子鑑定後發現，他並非女童生父，檢方另外查出，吳女6年前還曾與另一位賴姓男子發生婚外情，當時吳女與賴男各被判2月徒刑，吳女離婚後與李男結婚並改名。<br />\n<br />\n桃園地檢署認為，無證據顯示陳男知道愛上「不該愛的人」，且親子鑑定既認定陳男並非女童親生父親，難認有妨害家庭之嫌，偵結不起訴，另對吳女聲請簡易判決，至於女童生父到底是誰仍有待調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"f1123cd1aad1e0585a8d4ce34ab0b64c3dec19e5","tid":874191,"uid":149566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"個女有幾個爸爸"},{"pid":"fc768e3553d55197f384cd82559e1206fbffb857","tid":874191,"uid":47966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"李男<br />\n陳男<br />\n賴男<br />\n小王<br />\n<br />\n好亂喎"},{"pid":"41023111202afcdefa1ce60c5235e086cfc6685c","tid":874191,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc768e3553d55197f384cd82559e1206fbffb857","tid":874191,"uid":47966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"李男<br />\n陳男<br />\n賴男<br />\n小王<br />\n<br />\n好亂喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22069cf36f7605724df891ec7582283b84ae98eb","tid":874191,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc768e3553d55197f384cd82559e1206fbffb857","tid":874191,"uid":47966,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T04:36:11.000Z","msg":"李男<br />\n陳男<br />\n賴男<br />\n小王<br />\n<br />\n好亂喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T07:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://is3-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Video/v4/96/2c/28/962c287f-b6eb-8ab6-514f-dea80c2998d2/02356_MLPE_IL_MammaMiatheMovie_1400x2100.jpg/368x0w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis3-ssl.mzstatic.com%2Fimage%2Fthumb%2FVideo%2Fv4%2F96%2F2c%2F28%2F962c287f-b6eb-8ab6-514f-dea80c2998d2%2F02356_MLPE_IL_MammaMiatheMovie_1400x2100.jpg%2F368x0w.jpg&h=068caf71&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}